{"tid":1496184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"光復學校，圍堵革命","createTime":"2019-08-22T11:39:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T11:53:49.000Z","uid":254898,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0e204ac91a092cce2660d130684a123bba7194d2","tid":1496184,"uid":254898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:39:28.000Z","msg":"其實要9月罷課成功好簡單，<br />\n好多人唔罷課都係驚抽後算賬姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每間學校都起碼有700-800個學生，<br />\n咁你本身讀果間學校，只要有100-200人左右朝早著黑衫，<br />\n帶護頭gear(基本上頭盔口罩已經得，只係想學校認唔出係你)，<br />\n咁佢就冇辦法證明你既身份，就自然冇得抽稱你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直接包圍學校個出入口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n圍or塞本身要翻學個時段半個鐘至一個鐘左右，<br />\n咁校方自然會以太多示威者/市民聚集，<br />\n塞死左出入口，同時可能有危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而唔洗學生翻學架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n橫掂學生9月本身都要早起，<br />\n而家叫你由起身換校服改做換黑衫咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再驚既去附近間學校又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麻煩文宣覺得好既幫手整圖廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n九月罷課，學生自決。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KC1wFht.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKC1wFht.png&h=22757b95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n光復學校，圍堵革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n逆權運動，你我做起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcba5f638223dd27c97feb2bffd4685dda68def7","tid":1496184,"uid":254898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:40:27.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到post，覺得好既唔該幫幫手，比更多人有機會睇到。"},{"pid":"ae71fabcc6c7f7291c8eea27da675ce004d01230","tid":1496184,"uid":40641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:44:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">８２３人鏈主題曲上線喇！！！</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">《香港覺醒》<br />\nHong Kong Awakens</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1494949\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1494949</a>"},{"pid":"d656ae49a91157b44c170659fd0527b0f17db516","tid":1496184,"uid":258770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:47:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n帶護頭gear(基本上頭盔口罩已經得，只係想學校認唔出係你)，<br />\n咁佢就冇辦法證明你既身份，就自然冇得抽稱你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n其實教師日日對住d學生正係靠身型已經認得出"},{"pid":"94c73e99cd272eac715ec3aa06dd68ead159581a","tid":1496184,"uid":53029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:49:46.000Z","msg":"去人地間學校咪得囉"},{"pid":"d8d7859d8f81e9b290e75cba45107e7224852361","tid":1496184,"uid":254898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d656ae49a91157b44c170659fd0527b0f17db516","tid":1496184,"uid":258770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:47:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n帶護頭gear(基本上頭盔口罩已經得，只係想學校認唔出係你)，<br />\n咁佢就冇辦法證明你既身份，就自然冇得抽稱你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n其實教師日日對住d學生正係靠身型已經認得出"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:51:03.000Z","msg":"其實係學校門口逗留本身就冇犯校規，真係好驚既就switch去附近學校。<br />\n認得還認得，教師開唔開口還開唔開口，凡事講證據，有咩事就歡迎提供證據。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"882df95c8b5e58b91b7845f5ccd1d01443fab618","tid":1496184,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:51:41.000Z","msg":"罷課其實都唔應該迫9其他人罷<br />\n但要私補既開聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb79950e418ed7dc56102a081430468074691b5b","tid":1496184,"uid":254898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94c73e99cd272eac715ec3aa06dd68ead159581a","tid":1496184,"uid":53029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:49:46.000Z","msg":"去人地間學校咪得囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:51:50.000Z","msg":"所以講左一個point可以switch去附近學校，不過提防人數配合錯誤。"},{"pid":"958fb7aed252c3b9927d9e81e023fea1f0ef08b2","tid":1496184,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:52:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大大聲傳出去啊！！！<br />\n【我宣布】中秋開始罷工罷到支爆為止<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1495391\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1495391</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wERJGgC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwERJGgC.jpg&h=7d6f3fa7&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zA2HWPY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzA2HWPY.jpg&h=fa97f1b3&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wEtzNWE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwEtzNWE.jpg&h=b642e83c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43edf1b8c13b24847727a357206a254503187192","tid":1496184,"uid":254898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"882df95c8b5e58b91b7845f5ccd1d01443fab618","tid":1496184,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:51:41.000Z","msg":"罷課其實都唔應該迫9其他人罷<br />\n但要私補既開聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:53:49.000Z","msg":"主要針對有post指出元朗一間鄉議局學校唔比人罷課，唔比在校發表政治言論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但又講左句如果交通有問題會因情況處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}